      "type": "faq-content",
      "blocks": {
        "faq_item_t7Da3T": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "article": "faqs/how-was-oddballs-founded",
            "question_override": "How was OddBalls founded?",
            "answer_override": "<p>OddBalls launched in 2014, created to shake up the boring underwear market with bold, vibrant designs. Since day one, our mission has been to bring joy and comfort through colourful prints and top-quality products. OddBalls isn’t just about fun underwear—it’s about championing diversity and inclusion with something for everyone. Whether you're after boxers, briefs, knickers, or undies—call them what you like—we’ve got you covered.</p><p>Recognising our potential to do even more, we decided to use our bright, fun underwear to raise awareness for several charities as well as Testicular Cancer. We’re proud to have worked with amazing charities through partnerships with organisations like The OddBalls Foundation, Movember, Prostate UK, My Name’5 Doddie Foundation, Alzheimer’s Research UK and more.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_HRNtGN": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "article": "faqs/how-does-oddballs-support-charities",
            "question_override": "How does OddBalls support charities?",
            "answer_override": "<p>Recognising our potential to do even more, we decided to use our bright, fun underwear to raise awareness for several charities as well as Testicular Cancer. We’re proud to have worked with amazing charities through partnerships with organisations like The OddBalls Foundation, Movember, Prostate UK, My Name’5 Doddie Foundation, Alzheimer’s Research UK and more.</p><p>A portion of every sale from these collections is donated directly to the charity. Check the product description to see exactly how much your purchase contributes.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_DbFcTp": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "article": "faqs/what-is-the-oddballs-foundation",
            "question_override": "What is the OddBalls Foundation?",
            "answer_override": "<p>The OddBalls Foundation is our registered charity focused on raising awareness of testicular cancer. It runs university ambassador programmes, school visits, and educational campaigns—funded by profits and donations from our products.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_jhAj6X": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "article": "faqs/how-do-i-become-a-university-ambassador",
            "question_override": "How do I become a university ambassador?",
            "answer_override": "<p>If you're a student passionate about health and wellbeing, you can apply to become a University Ambassador through the OddBalls Foundation. You’ll spread awareness and join a movement of bold changemakers.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_iGzLkF": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "article": "faqs/can-i-collaborate-with-oddballs-as-an-influencer",
            "question_override": "Can I collaborate with OddBalls as an influencer?",
            "answer_override": "<p>We’re always up for creative partnerships! If you love the brand and share our values, visit our Affiliate page to sign up today.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
